<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h2>The road here</h2>
      <p>Four stops, one constant: communications in service of members.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline">

      <div class="stop reveal">
        <div class="yr">2016 &ndash; 2021</div>
        <h3>Digital Marketing Manager</h3>
        <p class="org">Long Island Board of REALTORS&reg;</p>
        <p>Communications lead for a regional REALTOR&reg; association serving thousands of members. Content, media outreach, and member communications, including the work below during the industry's hardest public moment.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="stop reveal">
        <div class="yr">2021 &ndash; 2022</div>
        <h3>Marketing Director</h3>
        <p class="org">Intero Showcase Properties</p>
        <p>Brand and communications for a residential real estate brokerage, producing public-facing campaigns and content in service of agents and their communities.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="stop reveal">
        <div class="yr">2022 &ndash; 2024</div>
        <h3>Digital Marketing Manager &rarr; Senior Manager</h3>
        <p class="org">eXp Realty</p>
        <p>Promoted within two years while leading communications and web across a global brokerage and its agent community, and building capability in-house rather than outsourcing it.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="stop now reveal">
        <div class="yr">2024 &ndash; Present</div>
        <h3>Director of Marketing &amp; Communications</h3>
        <p class="org">Sacramento Association of REALTORS&reg;</p>
        <p>Own the voice of a 7,000-member trade association across newsletters, email, social, press, and web. Built the communications function in-house after moving off an outside agency, and manage the small team that runs it.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
